primaryname":{"nameid":"2296356","name":"Ticket To Ride: Berlin","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Ticket To Ride: Berlin"},"alternatenames":[{"nameid":"2418209","name":"¡Aventureros al tren! Berlín"},{"nameid":"2297481","name":"Les Aventuriers du Rail: Berlin"},{"nameid":"2399449","name":"Ticket To Ride: Berlijn"},{"nameid":"2328341","name":"Wsiąść do Pociągu: Berlin"},{"nameid":"2329063","name":"Zug um Zug: Berlin","secondaryname":true}],"description":"<p>Welcome to the city of culture, arts and music! Discover Unter den Linden, and immerse yourself in the young cultural capital of Europe. Enjoy a sightseeing cruise on the river Spree, ride a bike through the Brandenburg Gate, or be amazed by the masterpieces displayed in the Pergamon Museum.</p>\n\n<p>In <em><strong>Ticket to Ride: Berlin</strong></em>, players race one another to visit the most iconic locations of the city and complete their Destination Tickets. The winning player will utilize Berlin's streetcars and, for the first time, will venture under the streets to incorporate a subway system into their routes.</p>\n\n","wiki":"<p>Contains:</p>\n\n<p>1 board map of Berlin&rsquo;s transportation network<br />\n44 Streetcars (11 in each color)<br />\n20 Subways (5 in each color)<br />\n44 Transportation cards<br />\n22 Destination Ticket cards<br />\n4 Scoring Markers<br />\n1 rule leaflet</p>\n\n<p>Microbadge: <a href=\"/microbadge/56074\"><img alt='Microbadge: Ticket to Ride: Berlin fan' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Ticket to Ride: Berlin fan', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_56074_0.png\"></a></p>\n\n<p>DETAILED COMPONENTS:<br />\nCardboard:<br />\n1 board map of Berlin&rsquo;s transportation network (59.5x21.5cm)</p>\n\n<p>Cardstock:<br />\n66 Cards (44x67mm):<br />\n44 Transportation cards<br />\n22 Destination Ticket cards</p>\n\n<p>Plastic:<br />\n44 Streetcars (11 in each color)<br />\n20 Subways (5 in each color)<br />\n1 spare Streetcar &amp; 1 spare Subway car of each color</p>\n\n<p>Wood:<br />\n4 Scoring Markers (disks; red, yellow, white, black)</p>\n\n<p>1 Rules leaflet (8 p. foldout).</p>\n\n","website":{"url":"https://www.daysofwonder.com/game/ticket-to-ride-berlin/","title":"Ticket to Ride: Berlin official webpage"},"imageid":"7508512","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__small/img/LMpNchnZoOX46Aj0GPcbI1ACuqk=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__micro/img/2_VGnj3uR-VD4xz1LuslX7ct7vE=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__square/img/gCw4YM4VZb0gEF8oVHOOKLAx8EU=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__tallthumb/img/cfRBmSA1hgGm9qcIBgSnm91xKgc=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__previewthumb/img/CMvKvwM4KwcOSZ7rZWz3bfOI7fw=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__square200/img/3_ZfS9XmNPa_QpoQDCwUsO63Vos=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__original/img/y33girl0FMzkMS-scnFlZkHJZeE=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic7508512.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/7508512/ticket-to-ride-berlin","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__itemrep/img/UO7TRnmVvY65EInV7ETff9ZuaMY=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","imageurl@2x":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/Ko8uw6JWAIC2K6wrnlr_1g__itemrep@2x/img/aSYgp2vzTFrgSKBlAgdhS8FBpnc=/fit-in/492x600/filters:strip_icc()/pic7508512.jpg","topimageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/unEB4WcuydfZMXpIU9Q0zQ__itemheader/img/8wvABNe7J-gymWk3zpks7VwEslc=/800x450/filters:quality(30):strip_icc()/pic7508534.png","imageSets":{"square100"